## MapR Converged Data Platform Demo
##### This is a live demo of fast streaming data on the MapR Converged Data Platform. We've developed an ETL pipeline with Kafka and Spark to process a real-time stock trading dataset. Press Shift-Enter to run.

result.msg:
MapR Converged Data Platform Demo

This is a live demo of fast streaming data on the MapR Converged Data Platform. We've developed an ETL pipeline with Kafka and Spark to process a real-time stock trading dataset. Press Shift-Enter to run.

paragraphs.title: Daily Trading Value ($) per Trader
paragraphs.text:
%sql SELECT sum(price*volume) TradingValue, streaming_ticks.sender senderID, substring(banks.name,0,14) name 
FROM streaming_ticks join banks on streaming_ticks.sender=banks.id
group by sender, name order by name desc
limit 500

paragraphs.title: Top 10 Most Active Traders
paragraphs.text: %sql SELECT streaming_ticks.sender ID, substring(banks.name,0,15) Name, count(1) TradesExecuted FROM streaming_ticks inner join banks on streaming_ticks.sender=banks.id group by streaming_ticks.sender, Name order by TradesExecuted desc limit 10

paragraphs.title: Share volume traded by "suspect traders"
paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT substring(date,11,20) time, SUM(volume) volume, suspect_traders.sender, banks.name 
FROM suspect_traders inner join banks on suspect_traders.sender=banks.id 
group by suspect_traders.sender, date, name order by date asc

paragraphs.title: Trading value ($) for "suspect traders"
paragraphs.text: %sql SELECT substring(date,11,20) time, SUM(price*volume) value, suspect_traders.sender, banks.name FROM suspect_traders inner join banks on suspect_traders.sender=banks.id group by suspect_traders.sender, date,name order by date asc

paragraphs.title: Trade Count per Trader
paragraphs.text:
%sql
-- THIS QUERY counts the number of trades each bank has participated in.
SELECT sender, symbol, count(1) trades_executed FROM streaming_ticks where symbol ="AA" group by sender, symbol order by sender

paragraphs.title: Price/Volume Profile for "suspect traders"

%sql 
SELECT price, volume,  streaming_ticks.sender, banks.name FROM streaming_ticks join banks on streaming_ticks.sender=banks.id where sender > "1159" AND sender < "1163" group by price, volume, sender, name order by price asc

paragraphs.title: Trading value ($) for selected traders
paragraphs.text:
%sql SELECT substring(date,11,20) time, SUM(price*volume) as trading_value, sender, banks.name 
FROM streaming_ticks inner 
join banks on streaming_ticks.sender=banks.id
where name=${Choose a Trader="Florida Business Bank","Florida Business Bank"|"RIVERVIEW COMMUNITY BANK"|"Campbell County Bank"|"First State Bank of Olmsted"} 
group by date, sender, name
order by date asc
